overview: With the lives of 62,000+ uninsured Idahoans at stake, a tiny grassroots team led by a married couple with a newborn and almost no political experience hit the road in a busted 1977 RV to campaign for Medicaid expansion. Somehow, it looks like they might even win.
tagline: Three friends. One 1977 Dodge. 62,000 lives on the line.
title: Reclaim Idaho
